The paper focuses on face detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of neural networks and machine learning techniques to improve the performance of face detection, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the importance of improving the accuracy and efficiency of face detection for security applications, which is related to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
